                  <title>The History of the Blessed Virgin Mary and the History of the Likeness of Christ which the Jews of Tiberias Made to Mock at. The Syriac Texts</title>
                  <citedRange>Londres, 1899, p. 3-146</citedRange>
               </bibl>
            </note>
